<abstract><t>This document defines the IPv6 CRH Helper option.  When an SRm6 ingress node originates a packet, it can use the IPv6 CRH Helper option to provide SID Forwarding Information Base (SFIB) information to downstream nodes that do not maintain a complete SFIB.</t></abstract>

